extends layout

block content
    h1 How to Sign Up
    p.lead
        | There's only on way to become a user on codepile: via <strong>pull request</strong>.
    p
        | More specifically:
        ol
            li
                | Fork <a href="https://github.com/larvalabs/codepile">this project</a> on github.
            li Add a feature, fix a bug, improve the design.
            li Add your github username to the <a href="https://github.com/larvalabs/codepile/blob/master/config/userlist.js">authorized user list</a>.
            li Submit a pull request. When we merge, you'll be a full user!
